title: Wiimms MKW-Fun 2014-04.v2.pal+ [RMCP25]
description:
OK, this is a pre-merged WBFS file for Wiimms excellent MKW-Fun custom Mario Kart tracks. It combines the standard Mario Kart game and his custom version with loads of new tracks!! Great if the kids (or you!) want a few more tracks to blast around...

Game Name: Wiimms MKW-Fun (Mario Kart World-Fun)
Release  : 2014-04
Game ID  : RMCP25 (different from standard Mario Kart, so can use both!)
Saves    : Different Licences from standard Mario Kart to prevent corruption
Format   : PAL
Language : ENGLISH

More info: http://wiki.tockdom.com/wiki/Wiimms_Mario_Kart_Fun_2014-04

I take *NO* credit for this game, just downloaded and merged/created it for my kids. This was a bit fiddly to do, and thought some people may not be able to do this (or have all the tools to do it), so I figured I would upload this to help them out.

If you like it, maybe buy a new Wii game to keep the franchise going as a thank-you for this freebie! :-)
